name: **Inishdawros – _Inis Damhraí_**
description: Inishdawros – Inis Damhraí L643-411 Sheet 44 Accessible on foot at LW, the inside channel on the E side provides great shelter to its N/S for smaller working boats. Nice beaches at S end and also at various stages of the tide elsewhere. Mallard. Rabbit.White cockles. Unspectacular. Nice outlook.
